name: com.android.bluetooth.pbap.BluetoothPbapService
description: To enable PBAP DEBUG/VERBOSE logging - run below cmd in adb shell, and restart com.android.bluetooth process. only enable DEBUG log: "setprop log.tag.BluetoothPbapService DEBUG"; enable both VERBOSE and DEBUG log: "setprop log.tag.BluetoothPbapService VERBOSE"
